{"tid":2157851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高雄市長補選　民進黨陳其邁以逾7成得票當選","createTime":"2020-08-15T10:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T11:01:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2d4b9acdfa4b6ece6b37532332dba4d04dd945","tid":2157851,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543916-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543916-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8W0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=11d2acf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543916-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3e89fd57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543916-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，高雄市長補選投票結束。<br />\n<br />\n選舉委員會公布，民進黨候選人陳其邁以超過67萬票當選，得票率超過7成。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨李眉蓁承認落敗，呼籲支持者給予陳其邁機會帶領高雄，又說市議會未來會繼續監督市長的工作。"},{"pid":"a8000ca63c78688c9bd06c1b47642e282f4a5bcc","tid":2157851,"uid":366076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"柯P：一黨專政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}